com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi

Interface LucentV11Address

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Address, CallCenterAddress, CallControlAddress, ITsapiAddress, LucentAddress, RouteAddress

    public interface LucentV11Address
extends LucentAddress
    The LucentV11Address interface extends LucentAddress with additional Avaya features. When a Provider is bound to a Avaya Communication Manager switch with PBX Driver Version 11 private data, this interface may be used to access additional capabilities.

    • Method Detail

      • getRegisteredEndpoints

        V11RegisteredEndpointInfo[] getRegisteredEndpoints()
                                            throws TsapiMethodNotSupportedException
        Gets a list of the endpoints currently registered to this Address.
        Returns:
        array of endpoints currently registered to this Address, or null if there was an error making the query (usually because the underlying device does not support this feature, like ACDs and VDNs)
        Throws:
        TsapiMethodNotSupportedException - if the provider does not support this feature.
